          h2.text-center(style='font-variant: small-caps;') this november 29th, come celebrate the robot parade and ball!
          p The Robot <span class='bold'>Parade</span> is a community event. We encourage everyone to dress in robot costume and parade through the Bywater with us. We will be hosting a costume making session for 4 hours immediately preceding the parade in conjunction with <a href='http://press-street.org/drawathon/'>Draw-a-thon</a>. The Parade is starting at <a href='https://www.google.com/maps/place/Marigny+Opera+House/@29.9647914,-90.0477018,18z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0000000000000000:0xfa03e1597122118e', target='_blank'>The Marigny Opera House</a> and going to <a href='https://www.google.com/maps/place/612+Piety+St,+New+Orleans,+LA+70117/@29.9623192,-90.0431748,19z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x8620a631dfd38d3b:0xa617c93de3735c5b', target='_blank'>The Old Iron Works</a>
      .row
