      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
          p The Robot <span class='bold'>Ball</span> is an art show immediately following the parade that celebrates invention. Tthe Ball is from 6 to 9 pm where there will be decadent food from the lovely Tres Bernard of <a href='https://www.facebook.com/WeveGotSoul'>Weâ€™ve got Soul</a>, delicious beverages, live music, and of course amazing art.. The atmosphere of the Ball is somewhere between art opening, science fair, and circus. 
          p Artists and makers are encouraged to make a robot to put in the parade. If you want to see what others in the community are working on, come to a Thursday night <a href='http://makersofno.la'>Makers of NO meet-up</a>.
          p Artists who are interested in putting art up at the Ball should send an email to: <a href='mailto:robotparadenola@gmail.com'>robotparadenola@gmail.com</a>
